# StudentApp - React Components

## Description

This project demonstrates the basic concept of React Components. It includes three reusable components:

- Home
- About
- Contact

These components are rendered inside the main App component.

## Technologies Used

- React
- JavaScript (ES6)
- HTML
- CSS
- Node.js
- npm

## Project Structure

```
studentapp
│
├── src
│   ├── Components
│   │   ├── Home.js
│   │   ├── About.js
│   │   └── Contact.js
│   │
│   ├── App.js
│   └── index.js
```

## Components

- Home Component
- About Component
- Contact Component

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/studentapp.git
cd studentapp
npm install
npm start
```

